title: Bobby
cast: Rishi Kapoor, Dimple Kapadia, Pran, Prem Nath, Sonia Sahni, Durga Khote, Aruna Irani, Prem Chopra, Farida Jalal
description: Raj, the son of strict, wealthy parents, falls in love with Bobby, the daughter of a poor Christian fisherman – a romance his parents oppose.

title: Charlotte's Web
cast: Debbie Reynolds, Charles Nelson Reilly, Paul Lynde, Henry Gibson, Rex Allen, Danny Bonaduce, Pamelyn Ferdin, Don Messick, Agnes Moorehead, Martha Scott, John Stephenson, Herb Vigran, Dave Madden
description: Follow the adventures of Wilbur the pig, Templeton the rat and Charlotte the spider in this animated musical version of E.B. White's timeless story.

title: Cleopatra Jones
cast: Tamara Dobson, Bernie Casey, BrendaSykes, Esther Rolle, Shelley Winters
description: A stylin' special agent chases down drug lords and does her part to stop trafficking. Soon, she finds herself seeking revenge on a dealer.

title: Enter the Dragon
cast: Bruce Lee, John Saxon, Jim Kelly, Ahna Capri, Kien Shih, Robert Wall, Angela Mao, Betty Chung, Geoffrey Weeks, Bolo Yeung, Peter Archer
description: Recruited by a British agent, Shaolin master Lee infiltrates a remote island and a brutal martial arts tournament to spy on a sinister crime lord.

title: Jealousy and medicine
cast: Mariusz Dmochowski, Ewa Krzyżewska, Włodzimierz Boruński, Andrzej Mrowiec, Józef Rosiński, Piotr Kąkolewski, Beata Nowicka, Edmund Fetting, Grażyna Staniszewska, Andrzej Łapicki
description: Tormented by mistrust, a businessman hires a cagey tailor to track his wife's whereabouts with her doctor only to send his mind further down an abyss.

title: Jimi Hendrix
cast: Jimi Hendrix, Eric Clapton, Billy Cox
description: Jimi Hendrix's family, friends, and fellow musicians discuss his life and influence. Hendrix also appears in classic performance footage.

title: Khoon Khoon
cast: Danny Denzongpa, Mahendra Sandhu, Rekha, Faryal, Helen, Jagdeep
description: As a crazed killer blazes a trail of blood through an anxious city, a hardened cop aims to take him down by any means in this remake of “Dirty Harry.”

title: Mean Streets
cast: Robert De Niro, Harvey Keitel, David Proval, Amy Robinson, Richard Romanus, Cesare Danova, Victor Argo, George Memmoli
description: In New York's Little Italy, a low-level hoodlum wrestles with loyalty to his mobster uncle, his faith and his friendship with an inveterate gambler.

title: The School of Mischief
cast: Suhair El-Babili, Adel Emam, Saeed Saleh, Younes Shalabi, Hadi El-Gayyar, Ahmad Zaki, Hassan Moustafa
description: A high school teacher volunteers to transform five notorious misfits into model students — and has unintended results.

title: Young Tiger
cast: Qiu Yuen, Charlie Chin, Jackie Chan, Hu Chin, Nan Chiang
description: Aided only by a tough female police officer, a Hong Kong taxi driver tries to escape from gangsters pursuing incriminating evidence left in his cab.
